            "heading": "🔴 Hard: Linear Self-Attention",
            "summary": "Implement **Linear Attention** — O(S·D²) instead of O(S²·D), enabling efficient long-sequence processing.\nReplace softmax with a **kernel feature map** $\\phi$:\n$$\\text{LinearAttn}(Q,K,V) = \\frac{\\phi(Q) \\left(\\phi(K)^T V\\right)}{\\phi(Q) \\cdot \\sum \\phi(K)}$$",
            "signature": "def linear_attention(Q, K, V):\n    # Q: (B, S, D_k), K: (B, S, D_k), V: (B, S, D_v)\n    # Returns: (B, S, D_v)",
